HEADWORD: Recommit
<hw>Re`com*mit"</hw> <pr>(-m?t")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To commit
again; to give back into keeping; specifically, to refer again to a
committee; <as>as, to <ex>recommit</ex> a bill to the same
committee</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

